Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}羅蘭德 王立軍事特殊學院
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪國人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像很凶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路小心點 弄傷人怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:55.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}追憶の扉を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:01:00.88,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}聞いていた音は囁き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:06.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}導いて魂の輪廻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:12.32,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一片の光の道へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:16.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}貫く痛みはInnocentre
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:20.99,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}信じたいよ 孤独じゃないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:26.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}ここは彷徨いParadise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:32.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}白く心染める翼で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:39.32,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}もし君の瞳に 辿り着けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:42.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}笑って 抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:48.71,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}生まれてきた意味を知れ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:52.27,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}見つめ合って 始まるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:56.28,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}Destiny in a jail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是為了讓我鬆懈大意？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}北方的勇者王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要轉移了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬琺還管他做啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都那麼說了你不覺得憋屈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那節課
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬琺害我沒逃成我才憋屈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}羅蘭德 城下街
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大甩賣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂花錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬琺有什麼想要的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是個14歲的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用強忍著的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊雅姐姐 姬琺姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布爾的間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還敢在這種地方嬉皮笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬琺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶蕾米爾逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬琺 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾獻上契約之文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿沉眠於大地的惡意之精獸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊雅姐姐她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會在國境上見的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的姐姐已經追上來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說不惜丟掉性命也要保護妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還能有何作為？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 姐姐會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…好 好難過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼…都聽你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了妹妹不惜出賣祖國的艾斯塔布爾間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對萊納…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我沒有資格說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我也會出賣萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想殺任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納你也睡太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}盧納帝國領 森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕車禁止打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不眠不休好久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的份他會幫你睡的 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}史特歐爾皇國 弗伊茲村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬琺·諾爾茲二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡撐不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有平民沒來得及避難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克軍馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為堪稱梅諾利斯大陸最強的軍事國家史特歐爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對萊納的複寫眼應該有一定研究
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能死在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾獻上契約之文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放舞於天空的光之魔獸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 魔法被彈開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施加了魔法防護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史特歐爾兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史特歐爾已經捨棄了這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人留下來又能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才痛恨戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你身為士兵卻痛恨戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上哪有人會喜歡戰爭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是裝作大吵大鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我露出破綻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的魔法 不是史特歐爾的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夾在加斯塔克和史特歐爾中間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救外國人而差點丟了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我就喜歡這種白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備就緒了 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民的保護工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史特歐爾軍的大規模魔法即將襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請陛下退避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也痛恨戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流血流淚 悲哀的事情全都不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭失去同伴 也討厭孩子們死去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更別說像你這種美女的死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了 絕不容許
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 只要有國家存在就會發生戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼怎樣做才能盡量減少這種犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是加斯塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有史特歐爾的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 拯救梅諾利斯大陸上所有人民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了消除戰爭而發動戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很矛盾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定 用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓吾回應汝的呼喚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 獻出代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此吾將釋放力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉我的左眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 給我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古洛威爾 釋放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這犧牲不會白費
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是殺戮者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃盡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去通知史特歐爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再遭到剛才那種攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就立即投降
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是代價
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用聖劍古洛威爾的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下已經失去了嗅覺和右腳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才奪去了難以計數的人命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以後拯救更多的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代價不過是一隻左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經算便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在後悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了人卻毫無悔意的那是人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你想拯救更多人命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就投靠我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投靠我加斯塔克之王 雷法爾·埃迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我會前往陛下身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷法爾·埃迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}羅蘭德王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎 之前的大肅清
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說那弗洛瓦德中將就是主謀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他連自己的父親也能下手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要讓我當元帥當到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你恢復元帥身份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我也能順理成章扔了這頭銜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆元帥閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您才是最適合的人選
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在忽悠我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得人一股無名火起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這一點正是統領軍隊的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種令人難以置信的單純
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此而生的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得士兵們甘願效忠於您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子是在耍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆還真是合不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望克拉烏·柯洛姆元帥 能去一趟艾斯塔布爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要重整艾斯塔布爾軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其編進羅蘭德軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布爾軍中還有很多人對羅蘭德心存芥蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要重組軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然會有人反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 經過那次肅清
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經有條件採取新措施了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事應當優先進行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:15:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和廣受艾斯塔布爾國民擁戴的諾婭·艾恩公主關係良好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事只有你辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要我利用諾婭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了這個國家好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下所說的這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包括我們艾斯塔布爾人民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也是我重要的國民
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企盼再也沒有戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這份心意絕無虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去 我有個同伴名叫姬琺·諾爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為艾斯塔布爾間諜的她出賣了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴們幾乎都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 陛下憎恨艾斯塔布爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使到現在 姬琺依然是我重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是不得已而為之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德殺害了她的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又抓了她妹妹當人質
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是被迫才成為雙重間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 她的笑容絕不是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定曾在心中無數次呼救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我卻沒有發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我還是國王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德和艾斯塔布爾就絕不會再戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我需要您的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事我都在所不辭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合併艾斯塔布爾軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強化我軍軍備的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提拔艾斯塔布爾軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也不失面子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是妙算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼順利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來將前往盧納帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去盧納？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃暗殺陛下的斯提亞里德公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎和盧納貴族有所勾結
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要去確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了我會傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謹記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}盧納帝國 雷吉特村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 這下要救可可也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們計劃和可可一起開盛大糰子派對的遠大夢想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你的夢想就這麼順勢成了我的夢想？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這遠大夢想 我將全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋裡好像沒人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感覺不到氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這不是萊納先生和菲莉絲小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能在這種地方重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這埋伏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我們對萊納先生很有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的複寫眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他持有者無可比擬的強大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的忘卻碎片和艾雷米奧之簪都完全不是對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你覺醒發狂之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能這樣恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了誰還這麼辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所救下的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是複寫眼持有者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們把他藏在哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然知道阿爾亞的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們對複寫眼有興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾獻上契約之文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿沉眠於大地的惡意之精獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是逃不過庫的攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧納兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵分兩路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我 你去保護阿爾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 萊納先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分別之前先告訴你一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位叫可可的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在被監禁在這個領地的貴族宅邸裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在那裡恭候大駕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}盧納帝國 王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧納帝國國王竟然不在國內
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王現在因病需要療養 離開了本國
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我失禮 請問國王去了何處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是北方的卡斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是奈爾法皇國呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 詳情我並不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性不問政事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃是此國淑女的傳統吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次前來能一睹美麗的公主芳容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已是不勝榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧納王背棄了和我羅蘭德的同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和加斯塔克聯手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不能見我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更有甚者 暗殺羅蘭德王的主謀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是盧納帝國國王其本人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把這些怪 怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克的使者一瞬間就殺光了盧納兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不能置之不理了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去收拾掉他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:04.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}忘れてたあの日の面影が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:10.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}空の向こう 微かに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:18.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心なら繋がっていたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:26.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}震えた瞳は答えずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:29.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに信じても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:33.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに伝えたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:39.31,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}この声は届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:44.08,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}光のフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:48.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}全てをこの体に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:54.19,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}歩き出す ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:57.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}記憶のセグメント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:03.29,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}今からまる運命の糸解き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:07.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}強くなりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:12.09,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}また出会えなら もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.38,0:23:19.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}守れるように 君を
